query:
INSERT INTO blocks (slot, blockhash, parent_slot, block_time, block_height)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
        ON CONFLICT (slot) 
        DO UPDATE SET
            blockhash = EXCLUDED.blockhash,
            parent_slot = EXCLUDED.parent_slot,
            block_time = EXCLUDED.block_time,
            block_height = EXCLUDED.block_height,
            processed_at = NOW()
